<lb n="0490b20" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0490b21" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 1325</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0490b22" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><note n="0490027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本</note>佛說療痔病經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0490b23" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0490b24" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0490028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔大〕－【三】</note><note n="0490028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔大〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0490028"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>唐三<note n="0490029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">藏＋（法師）【三】</note><note n="0490029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">藏＋（法師）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0490029"><lem wit="【大】">藏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">藏法師</rdg></app>義淨<note n="0490030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔奉制〕－【三】</note><note n="0490030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔奉制〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0490030"><lem wit="【大】">奉　制</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>譯</byline>
<lb n="0490b25" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0490b2501">如是我聞：</p><p id="pT21p0490b2505" place="inline">一時，薄伽梵在王舍大城竹林園
<lb n="0490b26" ed="T"/>中，與大苾芻眾五百人俱。</p><p id="pT21p0490b2611" place="inline">時，有眾多苾芻身
<lb n="0490b27" ed="T"/>患痔病，形體羸瘦、痛苦縈纏，於日夜中，極受
<lb n="0490b28" ed="T"/>憂惱。時，具壽阿難陀見是事已，詣世尊所，頂
<lb n="0490b29" ed="T"/>禮雙足，在一面立，<note n="0490031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">白＋（佛）【三】</note><note n="0490031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">白＋（佛）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0490031"><lem wit="【大】">白</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">白佛</rdg></app>言：「世尊！今王舍城多有
<pb n="0490c" ed="T" id="T21.1325.0490c"/>
<lb n="0490c01" ed="T"/>苾芻身患痔病，形體羸瘦、痛苦縈纏，於日夜
<lb n="0490c02" ed="T"/>中，極受憂惱。世尊！此諸<note n="0490032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">痔病＝病苦【三】</note><note n="0490032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">痔病＝病苦【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0490032"><lem wit="【大】">痔病</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">病苦</rdg></app>，云何救療？」</p><p id="pT21p0490c0216" place="inline"><note n="0490033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（爾時）＋佛【三】</note><note n="0490033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（爾時）＋佛【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0490033"><lem wit="【大】">佛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">爾時佛</rdg></app>
<lb n="0490c03" ed="T"/>告阿難陀：「汝可聽此《療痔病經》，讀誦受持、繫
<lb n="0490c04" ed="T"/>心勿忘，亦於他人，廣為宣說，此諸痔病，悉得
<lb n="0490c05" ed="T"/>除<note n="0490034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">差＝殄【三】</note><note n="0490034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">差＝殄【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0490034"><lem wit="【大】">差</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">殄</rdg></app>。所謂：風痔、熱痔、&CB00486;痔、三合痔、血痔、腹中
<lb n="0490c06" ed="T"/>痔、鼻內痔、齒痔、舌痔、眼痔、耳痔、頂痔、手足痔、
<lb n="0490c07" ed="T"/>脊背痔、<note n="0490035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">屎＝糞門【三】</note><note n="0490035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">屎＝糞門【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0490035"><lem wit="【大】">屎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">糞門</rdg></app>痔……遍身支節所生諸痔，如是痔&CB00485;，
<lb n="0490c08" ed="T"/>悉皆乾燥、墮落、消滅，<note n="0490036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">畢差＝必瘥【三】</note><note n="0490036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">畢差＝必瘥【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0490036"><lem wit="【大】">畢差</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">必瘥</rdg></app>無疑。皆應誦持如
<lb n="0490c09" ed="T"/>是神&CB00057;。」</p><p id="pT21p0490c0904" place="inline">即說&CB00057;曰：</p>
<lb n="0490c10" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0490c1001" type="dharani">「<note n="0490037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔怛姪…云〕二十五字－【三】</note><note n="0490037a" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔怛姪…訶〕二十字－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0490037a" word-count="20"><lem wit="【大】">怛姪他　揭賴米　室利　室利　魔揭室
<lb n="0490c11" ed="T"/>至　三磨&CB04133;都　莎訶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0490c12" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0490c1201">「<note n="0490037b" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔此&CB00057;丹藏云〕五字－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0490037b"><lem wit="【大】">此&CB00057;<note place="inline">丹藏云</note>：</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0490c13" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0490c1301" type="dharani">「怛姪他　頞闌帝　頞藍謎　室利鞞　室里
<lb n="0490c14" ed="T"/>室里　磨羯失質　三婆跋&CB00418;　莎訶</p>
<lb n="0490c15" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0490c1501">「阿難陀！於此北方，有大雪山王。中有大<note n="0490038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">莎＝娑【三】</note><note n="0490038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">莎＝娑【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0490038"><lem wit="【大】">莎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">娑</rdg></app>羅
<lb n="0490c16" ed="T"/>樹，名曰“難勝”。有三種華：一者初生、二者圓滿、
<lb n="0490c17" ed="T"/>三者乾枯。猶如彼華，乾燥落時，我<note n="0490039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">諸＋（苾芻所患）【三】</note><note n="0490039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">諸＋（苾芻所患）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0490039"><lem wit="【大】">諸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">諸苾芻所患</rdg></app>痔病亦
<lb n="0490c18" ed="T"/>復如是，勿復血出，亦勿膿流，永除苦痛，悉<note n="0490040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">皆＋（平復即令）【三】</note><note n="0490040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">皆＋（平復即令）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0490040"><lem wit="【大】">皆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">皆平復即令</rdg></app>
<lb n="0490c19" ed="T"/>乾燥。又復若常誦此經者，得<note n="0490041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">宿＋（命）【三】</note><note n="0490041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">宿＋（命）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0490041"><lem wit="【大】">宿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">宿命</rdg></app>住智，能憶過
<lb n="0490c20" ed="T"/>去七生之事。&CB00057;法成就，莎訶。」</p><p id="pT21p0490c2012" place="inline">又說&CB00057;曰：</p>
<pb n="0491a" ed="T" id="T21.1325.0491a"/>
<lb n="0491a01" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0491a0101" type="dharani">「怛姪他　<note n="0491001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">占米＝苫謎【宋】【明】＊，苦謎【元】＊</note><note n="0491001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">占米＝苫謎【宋】【明】＊，＝苦謎【元】＊</note><app n="0491001"><lem wit="【大】">占米</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】">苫謎</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">苦謎</rdg></app>　<app type="＊" source="0491001"><lem wit="【大】">占米</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】">苫謎</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">苦謎</rdg></app>　捨<note n="0491002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">占米＝苫謎【三】</note><note n="0491002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">占米＝苫謎【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0491002"><lem wit="【大】">占米</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">苫謎</rdg></app>　<note n="0491003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">占＝苫【宋】【明】，苦【元】</note><note n="0491003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">占＝苫【宋】【明】，＝苦【元】</note><app n="0491003"><lem wit="【大】">占</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】">苫</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">苦</rdg></app><note n="0491004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">沒&CB00135;＝末泥去【宋】【明】，末泥【元】</note><note n="0491004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">沒&CB00135;＝末泥去【宋】【明】，＝末泥【元】</note><app n="0491004"><lem wit="【大】">沒&CB00135;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】">末泥去</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">末泥</rdg></app>　捨
<lb n="0491a02" ed="T"/><note n="0491005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">占＝苫【三】</note><note n="0491005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">占＝苫【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0491005"><lem wit="【大】">占</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">苫</rdg></app>泥　莎訶」</p>
<lb n="0491a03" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0491a0301">佛說是經已，時，具壽阿難陀及諸大眾，皆大
<lb n="0491a04" ed="T"/>歡喜，信受奉行。</p>
<lb n="0491a05" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead>佛說療痔病經</jhead></juan></div1>
